17 to the tenant by certified mail, return receipt requested, at the tenant’s last known address,
18 and also by first–class mail to the title agent or attorney listed on the deed to the property
19 or the intake sheet recorded with the deed, a bill for the ground rent due, may bring an
20 action for possession of the property under § 14–108.1 of this article[; if].
